e.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/TheKillsAlison-Mosshart-Donald-Trump.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/TheKillsAlison-Mosshart-Donald-Trump-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/TheKillsAlison-Mosshart-Donald-Trump-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/TheKillsAlison-Mosshart-Donald-Trump-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/TheKillsAlison-Mosshart-Donald-Trump-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/TheKillsAlison-Mosshart-Donald-Trump-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-kills">Kills</a>乐队主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alison-mosshart">艾莉森·莫斯哈特 (Alison Mosshart)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/mark-hamill-among-celebrities-evacuated-during-california-wildfires-3827144">在加州持续发生山火</a>之际猛烈抨击<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump)</a> ，称一旦他掌权，重建社区将“更加困难”。</p><p>这位在洛杉矶拥有一处房产的创作型歌手今天（1 月 9 日）在 Instagram 上分享了一条信息，其中她向受影响的人们传达了“爱和极端的精神毅力”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-kills-jamie-hince-alison-mosshart-interview-god-games-indie-sleaze-guitar-music-3521216">The Kills：“为什么嘻哈音乐应该面向未来，而吉他音乐应该总是回顾过去？”</a></strong></li></ul><p>周二（1 月 7 日）在洛杉矶开始的山火迅速演变成不同社区的五场同时火灾，导致超过 15 万居民逃离家园。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">爱莉安娜·格兰德 (Ariana Grande)</a>都在社交媒体上分享了资源链接。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">来自娱乐界的其他人物</a>也详细讲述了他们的疏散经历，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/star-wars"><em>《星球大战》</em></a>演员马克·哈米尔和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paris-hilton">帕丽斯·希尔顿</a>。</p><p>莫斯哈特写道：“我彻夜未眠前往洛杉矶。这超出了灾难性，这些火灾，一场火灾风暴，一场真正的噩梦，但即使这些词与推平美国第二大城市的痛苦相比也算不了什么。一座我深深热爱的城市。</p><p> “我很感谢我的邻居，他们在我跨越半个国家时一直通过电话向我通报我的邻居的最新情况，也感谢我亲爱的朋友@erinmariedean，他专程到我家来保存尽可能多的艺术品。在一切都可能失去的情况下尽可能地行动。”</p><p>这位在佛罗里达州长大、在田纳西州纳什维尔拥有一所房子的歌手表示，她“很幸运能够在她的生活中遇到伟大的人”，并补充道：“非常幸运。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEmQAmnuNSj/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 54