s/2025/01/Heartworms@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Heartworms@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/heartworms">Heartworms</a>分享了一首不祥的新单曲，名为“Extraordinary Wings”。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/heartworms-the-cover-interview-glutton-for-punishment-3826193">Heartworms 是南伦敦正在崛起的哥特式巨星</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位南伦敦艺术家和<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/heartworms-the-cover-interview-glutton-for-punishment-3826193"><em>NME</em>封面明星</a>的新单曲是她备受期待的专辑《Glutton For Punishment》的最新预览。首张专辑将于 2 月 7 日通过 Speedy Wunderground 发行。</p><p>伴随着由经常合作者吉尔伯特·特雷霍 (Gilbert Trejo) 执导的音乐视频，这首新单曲紧随<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heartworms-drops-stirring-new-single-warplane-and-announced-debut-album-glutton-for-punishment-3802592">《战机》</a>之后推出，并继续向歌手对军用飞机的热爱致敬。</p><p> “<em>你有鸟儿的意图/教我像那样飞翔/你突然来到我身边/现在你在这里，我喜欢这样</em>，”随着歌曲的发展，她开始唱。 “<em>我没有时间告诉你我想听什么/这就是为什么我捂住双耳/你的意图是我害怕的鸟</em>。”</p><p>看看下面。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="心丝虫 - 非凡的翅膀（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/5htIIBUG0Es?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在谈到即将发行的专辑时，这位艺术家（真名 Jojo Orme）解释了她如何比广受好评的 2023 年 EP《A Comforting Notion》更进一步地推动自己。</p><p> “在我的 EP 中，人们将我归类为后朋克，”她解释道。 “我当时想，‘酷，我可以做到这一点，但我还可以做得更多’——我可以做后朋克，但我也可以流行和朗朗上口，这张专辑代表了这一点。我想人们听到这个消息时可能会感到惊讶。”</p><p>这张唱片由长期合作者 Dan Carey 制作，还将向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/depeche-mode">Depeche Mode</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pj-harvey">PJ Harvey</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a>等艺术家致敬，创造出新闻稿所描述的“完全是 Heartworms 的强大声音冲击”。</p><p>它由九首歌曲组成，还探讨了破碎的家庭和破碎的关系的主题，以及拥抱混乱的感觉。 “我们都非常喜欢惩罚自己，我总是喜欢唱歌并思考它，”奥姆说。<a href="https://heartworms.ffm.to/glutton-for-punishment" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处预订专辑。</a> </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DEmjYcnSrTS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.02