含“发自肺腑的情感和半开玩笑的幽默、毁灭、嬉戏和全身心投入的感觉”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3796629" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3796629" style="width: 3000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3796629" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DivorceDriveTo-Goldenhammer-album-cover-art.jpg" alt="离婚 - &#39;Drive To Goldenhammer&#39; 官方专辑封面" width="3000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DivorceDriveTo-Goldenhammer-album-cover-art.jpg 3000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DivorceDriveTo-Goldenhammer-album-cover-art-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DivorceDriveTo-Goldenhammer-album-cover-art-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DivorceDriveTo-Goldenhammer-album-cover-art-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DivorceDriveTo-Goldenhammer-album-cover-art-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DivorceDriveTo-Goldenhammer-album-cover-art-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DivorceDriveTo-Goldenhammer-album-cover-art-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3796629" class="wp-caption-text"> Divorce – “Drive To Goldenhammer”官方专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>“我们对《驶向金锤》感到非常自豪。我们必须按照我们想要的方式制作一张专辑，保留奇怪的部分，遵循温暖，但不要想太多，”Divorce 在之前的一份声明中说道。</p><p> “这张专辑向寻找地方和家致敬；伟大的人类平等者之一。生活的大部分内容都与这种特殊的需求相矛盾。还有金锤；你是继续开车的理由。我们会一次又一次地找到你！”</p><p> 《离婚》将于今年春天在英国和爱尔兰进行一场头条巡演，最后在伦敦 KOKO 举办一场演出。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fdivorce-tickets%2Fartist%2F5421796" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到所有剩余的门票</a>，并查看下面的完整时间表。</p><h3> <strong>Divorce 2025 年英国/爱尔兰巡演日期为：</strong></h3><p><strong>行进</strong><br /><strong>27 - 布林登，牛津</strong><br /><strong>28 - 奇怪的啤酒，布里斯托尔</strong><br /><strong>29 – 城堡与猎鹰酒店，伯明翰</s