tent/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在播出两季并在世界各地推出多个版本之后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-traitors"><em>《叛徒》</em></a>仍然是电视上收视率最高的真人秀节目之一。</p><p>第三季由克劳迪娅·温克尔曼 (Claudia Winkleman) 主持，25 名参赛者在苏格兰高地的一座城堡里争夺高达 12 万英镑的奖金。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/best-tv-shows-2025-stranger-things-bear-andor-wednesday-3826471">2025 年值得期待的 20 部大型电视节目</a></strong></li></ul><p>在城堡里，几名参赛者被选为“叛徒”，他们必须隐藏自己的身份并消灭“忠实者”才能获得奖品。然而，如果忠实者能够通过每日圆桌会议驱逐所有叛徒，那么所有幸存的参赛者都将赢得现金奖励。</p><p> BBC 去年续订了该剧第四季，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-uk-celebrity-edition-announced-3786092">九集的名人版</a>也在筹备中。</p><h2>谁在第一周就离开了<em>《叛徒》</em>第三季？</h2><p>开场一集介绍了所有 25 名参赛者，尽管他们在踏入城堡之前就经历了火车车厢的扭曲。三名参赛者不得不提名自己离开火车，不知道结果会是什么。</p><p>选择下车的选手是Alexander Dragonetti、Fozia Fasil和Jack Marriner-Brown，他们都被暂时从比赛中除名。</p><p><strong>被杀：尹律（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827330" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827330" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827330" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的尹律" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827330" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的吕茵（图片来源：BBC 和兰伯特工作室）</figcaption></figure><p>由于叛徒们受到她作为传播学博士的怀疑和智慧的威胁，尹律成为第三季中第一个被谋杀的参赛者。</p><p><strong>被放逐：内森·海德（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827328" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827328" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827328" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg" alt="内森在《叛徒》中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827328" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的内森 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管圆桌会议上对叛徒琳达的怀疑越来越多，八名玩家还是投票罢免了 39 岁的房地产顾问内森。除了他安静的举止之外，这个决定所依据的证据很少。</p><p><strong>被谋杀者：基思·斯图尔特（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827333" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827333" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827333" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的基思" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827333" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的基思 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>窗户清洁工基思被认为是该组织中坚强而可爱的角色，他成为第二个被叛徒谋杀的人。</p><p><strong>被放逐：艾伦·温（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827334" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827334" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827334" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的艾伦" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827334" class="wp-caption-text">艾伦在《叛徒》中被放逐（图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert）</figcaption></figure><p>在被其他玩家认为可疑，再加上她相信大多数叛徒都是“坚强的女性”后，翻译埃伦被逐出游戏。</p><p> “一旦你的名字被曝光，你就很难自救，”她告诉<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/crrw4d1lxygo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>。</p><p><strong>被放逐：Armani Gouveia（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827329" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827329" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827329" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的阿玛尼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827329" class="wp-caption-text">阿玛尼是第三季第一个离开的叛徒 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在第三集中，玩家们成功地驱逐了他们的第一个叛徒，因为阿玛尼的傲慢和指挥方式很快就对她产生了不利影响。在她自己的妹妹玛雅·古维亚 (Maia Gouveia) 承认对她的行为表示怀疑后，她的命运就注定了。</p><h2>第二周谁离开了？</h2><p>在第二周剧集开始时，之前被淘汰的参赛者亚历山大·德拉戈内蒂、福齐亚·法西尔和杰克·马里纳-布朗被带回来参加挑战，他们被吊在森林的笼子里。</p><p>玩家只能拯救三名悬挂参赛者中的两名，然后他们将从此时开始加入游戏。在提出令人信服的论据后，亚历山大和福齐亚被玩家救了出来，而出生于约克郡的市场交易员<strong>杰克则被送回家</strong>。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：玛雅·古维亚（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827331" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827331" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827331" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的玛雅" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827331" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的玛雅 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在她的妹妹在最后一次圆桌会议上被放逐后，叛徒们选择谋杀玛雅，以消灭可能是强大的对手。她的死也让弗雷迪产生了怀疑，弗雷迪此前曾在上一次圆桌会议上针对她。</p><p><strong>被放逐：卡西姆·艾哈迈德（忠实者）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827327" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827327" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827327" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的卡西姆" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827327" class="wp-caption-text">卡西姆被放逐让所有人都感到沮丧 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>不幸的是，卡西姆不可避免地被逐出小组，因为他太友善了，而且——至少在杰克看来——因为他是一名医生。阿玛尼是在上一次圆桌会议上决定他命运的人，因为她莫名其妙地为他担保，让其他玩家相信他也是叛徒。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-season-3-who-was-killed-3827323">本周《叛徒》中谁被杀？</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
安迪·贝尔 (Andy Bell) 宣布推出第三张个人专辑《Pinball Wanderer》，与前绿洲乐队成员 Gem Archer 合作https://www.nme.com/news/music/andy-bell-announces-solo-album-pinball-wanderer-featuring-former-oasis-bandmate-gem-archer-3827436?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=andy-bell-宣布独奏专辑-pinball-wanderer-featuring-前 oasis-bandmate-gem-archerTom Skinner Thu, 09 Jan 2025 10:36:48 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3827436 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安迪·贝尔新闻图片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这张“夜间唱片”已由 Dot Allison 和 Neu! 的 Michael Rother 合作预览</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andy-bell-announces-solo-album-pinball-wanderer-featuring-former-oasis-bandmate-gem-archer-3827436">安迪·贝尔 (Andy Bell) 宣布与前 Oasis 乐队成员 Gem Archer 合作的第三张个人专辑《Pinball Wanderer》</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次亮相。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安迪·贝尔新闻图片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/AndyBellnewalbum-Oasis-single-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andy-bell">安迪·贝尔 (Andy Bell)</a>宣布推出一张名为“Pinball Wanderer”的新个人专辑，其中包括他的前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>乐队成员和长期合作者 Gem Archer。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ride">Ride</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mantra-of-the-cosmos">Mantra of the Cosmos</a>成员将于 2 月 28 日星期五通过 Sonic Cathedral 发行他的第三张个人唱片。<a href="https://linktr.ee/pinballwanderer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此预订/预保存</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ride-share-blissful-single-peace-sign-and-tell-us-about-new-album-interplay-3566131">骑行分享幸福单曲“Peace Sign”并告诉我们新专辑“Interplay”</a></strong></li></ul><p>他已经预演了即将推出的项目“I&#39;m In Love…”——翻唱了 The Passions 乐队的经典后朋克单曲“I&#39;m in Love With A German Film Star”（1981）。贝尔对这首歌曲的演绎以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dot-allison">Dot Allison</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/neu">Neu!</a>的梦幻嗓音为特色。迈克尔·罗瑟 (Michael Rother) 弹吉他。</p><p> “我在每次 Ride 试音时都经历了弹奏那首歌的吉他部分的阶段，”贝尔在一份声明中解释道。 “ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/erol-alkan">Erol Alkan</a>一直坚持其‘原始鞋注’，我同意。”</p><p>他继续说道：“多特已经是我很长时间的朋友了。像许多特定年龄段的人一样，我喜欢“One Dove”，大约 2004 年，当我在瑞典的一个俱乐部之夜为她预订 DJ 时，她在凌晨 3 点演奏了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/motorhead">Motörhead</a>的“黑桃 A”，从而扳平了位置，我们成了伙伴们。我演奏了她上一张专辑“Consciousology”中的一些曲目，这是她的回报。</p><p> “然后，令人难以置信的是，来自 Neu 的迈克尔·罗瑟！也结束了它。去年二月，我在巴比肯艺术中心的演出中遇见了他，并请他重新混音这首歌，但他却决定弹吉他，这将一切提升到了一个全新的水平。”</p><p>他补充道：“第二天早上我要去巡演，我知道在离开之前我必须对这首单曲进行混音。在混音中听到迈克尔的吉他部分真是一种难以置信的感觉；它只是激励我继续录音并混入夜晚。”</p><p>在这里听“我恋爱了……”： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="安迪·贝尔的壮举。多特·艾利森和迈克尔·罗瑟“我恋爱了……”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EW9czxT_8Tg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>贝尔还得到<a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=High+Flying+Birds+NME+news&amp;sca_esv=be7123bc69849c3e&amp;sxsrf=ADLYWILHrxF7X8BpT1IiLS43l7xHt0IYEg%3A1736416032708&amp;ei=IJt_Z4X6KsSwhbIPpajh-Ag&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiFir_mreiKAxVEWEEAHSVUGI8Q4dUDCBA&amp;uact=5&amp;oq=High+Flying+Birds+NME+news&amp;gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiGkhpZ2ggRmx5aW5nIEJpcmRzIE5NRSBuZXdzMgUQIRigAUjHBVAZWPMEcAF4AZABAJgBtQGgAZAEqgEDMy4yuAEDyAEA-AEBmAIGoAKyBMICChAAGLADGNYEGEfCAg0QABiABBiwAxhDGIoFwgIOEAAYsAMY5AIY1gTYAQHCAhMQLhiABBiwAxhDGMgDGIoF2AEBwgIHEAAYgAQYDcICBhAAGBYYHsICBxAhGKABGAqYAwDiAwUSATEgQIgGAZAGELoGBggBEAEYCZIHAzQuMqAHpRY&amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp">High Flying Birds</a>成员 Gem Archer 的协助，后者在 1999 年至 2009 年间与贝尔一起在 Oasis 演出<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552">。有传言称，两人将</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-more-dates-added-to-2025-tour-due-to-unprecedented-demand-3788543"><em>Oasis Live &#39;25</em>大型重聚巡演</a>中与 Liam 和 Noel Gallagher 在舞台上重聚。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-more-dates-added-to-2025-tour-due-to-unprecedented-demand-3788543">今年</a>。</p><p> “这张专辑是从鼓点开始的。我喜欢打鼓，而 Gem 非常擅长录制鼓，”贝尔说道。 “所有的旋律和歌词都是由此而来。”</p><p>根据一份新闻稿，《Pinball Wanderer》为贝尔带来了“新的声音篇章”——继他之前的两张个人唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rides-andy-bell-shares-video-for-new-solo-track-i-was-alone-2754224">《The View From Halfway Down》</a> （2020 年）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andy-bell-announces-his-new-solo-album-flicker-and-shares-something-like-love-3134890">《Flicker》</a> （2022 年）之后。</p><p>这张专辑从去年夏天的半成品到完成录制和混音，经历了“一次紧张的通宵录音”，被称为“一张典型的夜间唱片”。</p><p> “[它]是迷幻旋律、Can via The <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-stone-roses">Stone Roses</a>节奏和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arthur-russell">Arthur Russell</a>风格的实验纹理的混合体，非常适合用耳机聆听的时刻以及穿越最酷、最低调的舞池，”它继续说道。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552">支持我：2025 年绿洲阵容中的所有球员</a></strong></li></ul><p>此外，贝尔还透露，他“从<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/turnstile">Turnstile</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/turnstile-glow-on-review-3022461">《Glow On》</a>中汲取灵感，创作了一些太短的歌曲”。歌曲“Madder Lake Deep”被描述为“水彩画中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cocteau-twins">Cocteau Twins</a> ”，而“Apple Green UFO”则参考了<em>《辛普森一家》</em>和<em>《外星人》</em> 。</p><p> “我在原声音乐上演奏了这首即兴重复段，有点像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">齐柏林飞艇的</a>民谣歌曲，但我把它带入了 Serge Gainsbourg 的世界，并给了它一杯苦艾酒，”他在谈到后一首歌时解释道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEmgz3_sLAQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/s